{"tid":1011511,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【撇低妻女去團拜】王浩信相約唐詩詠拜年 伍允龍慘變路人","createTime":"2019-02-06T22:17:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T08:56:50.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e46ab5eb236baa06d16d8cf0843daddea39f3909","tid":1011511,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T22:17:25.000Z","msg":"大台劇集《解決師》剛在去年底拍完，劇中演員王浩信及唐詩詠等今日相約團拜，不過這次團拜還多了一個伍允龍，而他更被唐詩詠取笑是路人。<br />\n今日年初二，很多藝人也仍在放假中，就好像王浩信、唐詩詠等，今日就相約同劇的張曦雯，以及伍允龍一起團拜，而王浩信於Ig貼出照片，寫着：「年初二 #解決師 與 #兄弟仝人祝大家，新春快樂，一團和氣，心想事成，萬事勝意，龍馬精神，步步高升，珠聯璧合，恭喜恭喜！」只見四人心情大好，不時擺出功夫甫士。<br />\n雖然在王浩信眼中，伍允龍是他拍劇集《兄弟》中的親兄弟，但他在唐詩詠眼中則是路人，唐更笑言：「解決師團拜，多咗個路人」。<br />\n早前王浩信老婆陳自瑤，曾表示自己農曆新年只有3日假期，未知團拜過後，他是否會趕回家跟老婆及囡囡一起過新年呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190206/large/1549443293_500f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190206%2Flarge%2F1549443293_500f.jpg&h=69f59515&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190206/large/1549443298_7229.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190206%2Flarge%2F1549443298_7229.jpg&h=70558aa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190206/large/1549443293_cfe5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190206%2Flarge%2F1549443293_cfe5.jpg&h=ae988461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190206/large/1549443293_a8dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190206%2Flarge%2F1549443293_a8dc.jpg&h=d51b6559&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190206/large/1549443297_4665.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190206%2Flarge%2F1549443297_4665.jpg&h=cd6fddab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190206/large/1549443298_af88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190206%2Flarge%2F1549443298_af88.jpg&h=092531f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f00bdb42dc42820c4001f625dc9e60d5f7e49bd1","tid":1011511,"uid":152123,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T22:29:35.000Z","msg":"好似dodo姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eb766b7c763e2f95baa52cbda438d6135da0455","tid":1011511,"uid":3177,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f00bdb42dc42820c4001f625dc9e60d5f7e49bd1","tid":1011511,"uid":152123,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T22:29:35.000Z","msg":"好似dodo姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T22:41:41.000Z","msg":"exact7ly"},{"pid":"d42768ede851b67f7ff3a3fd6409446327ee058b","tid":1011511,"uid":7206,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T23:04:10.000Z","msg":"佢算唔算典型吊高黎賣擺到過晒期先知出事嘅港女之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd6760f22c47a876f1ee5437162b349904107513","tid":1011511,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T00:07:47.000Z","msg":"律政強人有未整容樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca5040e63fd039e3b512f9ca0f3fc1d9aeb2f8cf","tid":1011511,"uid":38416,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T00:12:15.000Z","msg":"張曦雯三十歲未到就咁既樣 <br />\n唔通浸過咸水真係易殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44bf19dca746d9f6f38764e5b0c35c2b56615a4d"